&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://static.googleusercontent.com/media/landing.google.com/zh-CN//sre/static/pdf/Building_Secure_and_Reliable_Systems.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;2020-Building Secure &amp;amp; Reliable Systems 📚&lt;/a&gt;: Best Practices for Designing, Implementing and Maintaining Systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
